    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've heard the \"hope\" speech before, but it just feels fake. everything i did was for someone else, and now that he's gone, there's just this massive hole where my life used to be. it feels so heavy. like i'm just a shell. honestly, why should i even keep trying to fight this feeling when it's just going to keep being this heavy? it feels like the only way to actually get some peace is to just stop.",
